Device ID: S138 Calibration 8552 Kitting 70 lb counter scale As Found O.O.T. See attached cert.  As Left passed.  Scale S138 was out of tolerance at 50 lb -.030 lb & at 70 lb -.035 lb.  S138 is in calibration to 35 lb.  When kitting heavier parts 1-5 parts are weighed to get the total number of parts in a box.  This weight does not exceed 30 lb.  A few examples: 0910561-01 for 28704-1 casting weighs 4.1 lb x (5) = 20.5 lb.4610174-01 for 32775-1 casting weighs 5.6 lb x (5) = 28 lb.0610182-02 for 25923-1 casting weighs 8 lb x (2) = 16 lb0610183-02 for 25923-1 casting weighs 3.3 lb x (5) = 16.5 lb  Conclusion:Since scale S138 is in calibration to kitting count weights & parts are re-counted after molding, there is no risk to the customer.

Device ID: S138 Calibration 9133 Kitting 70 lb counter scale As Found O.O.T. see attached cert.  As Left passed.  Scale S138 was out of tolerance at 50 lb .020 lb & at 70 lb .045 lb.  S138 is in calibration to 35 lb.  When kitting heavier parts 1-5 parts are weighed to get the total number of parts in a box.  This weight does not exceed 30 lb.  A few examples:0910561-01 for 28704-1 casting weighs 4.1 lb x (5) = 20.5 lb.4610174-01 for 32775-1 casting weighs 5.6 lb x (5) = 28 lb.0610182-02 for 25923-1 casting weighs 8 lb x (2) = 16 lb.0610183-02 for 25923-1 casting weighs 3.3 lb x (5) = 16.5 lb.Conclusion:Since scale S138 is in calibration to kitting count weights & parts are re-counted after molding, there is no risk to the customer.
